<h1>Terms of Service</h1>

<p>These Terms govern your use of the <strong>OTG Player Tracker</strong> Discord bot (“<em>Bot</em>”). By invoking the Bot in any Discord server, you agree to these Terms.</p>

<h2>1. Description</h2>
<p>The Bot builds Tracker.gg profile links (and, when available, basic stats) for the game <em>Off The Grid</em>.</p>

<h2>2. Eligibility &amp; Discord Compliance</h2>
<ul>
  <li>You must comply with <a href="https://discord.com/terms" target="_blank">Discord Terms of Service</a> and <a href="https://discord.com/guidelines" target="_blank">Community Guidelines</a>.</li>
  <li>Server administrators may remove or restrict the Bot at any time.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Acceptable Use</h2>
<ul>
  <li>No spamming, flooding, or automated abuse of slash commands.</li>
  <li>No attempts to reverse‑engineer, exploit, or modify the Bot.</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. Third‑Party Services</h2>
<p>The Bot links to <a href="https://tracker.gg/" target="_blank">Tracker.gg</a>. All data displayed there is subject to Tracker Network’s own Terms and Privacy Policy.</p>

